newCmd('.star','','*v+10.2 -- new;','The <b>star</b> command places a set of crosshairs of a given size in Angstroms on the selected atoms. The default size of the star is, like spacefill, the nominal van der Waals radius for the atom. The default color for the star is that of the atom it is associated with. Use {#.color~color star [colorname]} to then color selected stars the color of your choice.','1|1','','')
